author: National Geographic
description:
Hurricane Katrina looms over New Orleans, while residents face a chaotic evacuation. As the city scrambles to prepare, 100,000 are left behind.

Hurricane Katrina: Race Against Time, a docuseries from Ryan Coogler and Traci Curry, looks back at the unprecedented tragedy on its 20th anniversary through images, witness accounts, and interviews.
